snippet.title: Heart Chain Kitty - Adventure Kitten Skills (Trailer)
snippet.description:
This trailer of my game Heart Chain Kitty shows off many of Kittey's abilities and gimmicks. The game is a continuation of my video game series A Game with a Kitty and Darkside Adventures. 

Steam Store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/933210/Heart_Chain_Kitty/

Most of my old games are free to download at http://www.origamihero.com.
